                            <p><strong>Equity method: consolidation entries</strong></p>
                            <p>As in case of equity method the software doesn't  transfer any figures from associates reporting to parent reporting, the entire  consolidation is made with adjustment entries (they can be different in each individual  case, that is why user needs to make them with due consideration): </p>
