                                        <p style="font-weight:bold; margin-left:0cm">FP: Goodwill</p>
                                        <p style="font-weight:normal; margin-left:0.5cm">Additional recognition, goodwill</p>
                                        <p style="font-weight:normal; margin-left:0.5cm">Gross carrying amount, goodwill</p>
                                        <p style="font-weight:normal; margin-left:0.5cm">[Goodwill from business combination]</p>
                                    </td>
                                    <td valign="top" class="periods textlable">
                                        <p style="font-weight:bold; margin-left:0cm">FP: Retained earnings</p>
